{"tid":670013,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"做亞軍好啲？曼聯搵錢多過曼城","createTime":"2018-05-19T03:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T21:45:22.000Z","uid":54373,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d3453e1c4530532ae3aa9f3018f993a9f670b39c","tid":670013,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:44:52.000Z","msg":"【新增動新聞】<br />\n英國《BBC》報道，儘管曼城以19分之差在今季英超封王，但藍月亮所賺得的錢，竟然比只得聯賽亞軍的曼聯少。<br />\n<br />\n根據報道，曼聯今季賺得1億4,977萬鎊（約15.89億港元），比英超冠軍曼城多出超過320,000鎊，這是由於曼聯今季的電視直播賽事比曼城多兩場，達到28場，與阿仙奴和利物浦看齊，紅魔鬼單是這方面已經因此多收226萬鎊。<br />\n<br />\n英超球隊今季收入（只列前6位）<br />\n1.曼聯　1億4,977萬鎊<br />\n2.曼城　1億4,944萬鎊<br />\n3.利物浦　1億4,590萬鎊<br />\n4.熱刺　1億4,445萬鎊<br />\n5.阿仙奴　1億4,204萬鎊<br />\n6.車路士　1億4,171萬鎊"},{"pid":"bb1c917353baed9dac1bc0cdb146eb399fd793ed","tid":670013,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9030c987e9b2a2c74b098096c90d135cd35fe71a","tid":670013,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:51:20.000Z","msg":"再係咁既戰績<br />\n好快超越"},{"pid":"0af1892982b52644dc4821638c277e6ab1fd40d9","tid":670013,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:53:01.000Z","msg":"有冇盈利數字？"},{"pid":"250d7ef61bc83103be3e079d7458ebe1d3959644","tid":670013,"uid":5843,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:54:08.000Z","msg":"講賺錢性價比阿仙奴有爺爺實贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1ae72b2af13171f1390c146575387f2c5405a2","tid":670013,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:11:21.000Z","msg":"我地曼城真係唔敢同曼聯鬥錢多<br />\n人地話晒最賺錢球會"},{"pid":"cf93c50944faec6dc95a4f3faafb7a3fb5ba439f","tid":670013,"uid":2688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:12:12.000Z","msg":"其實6隊都差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"